{"TopicId":75560,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"If you could only install 3 KSP mods... which 3 would it be?","CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-06-20T13:51:33Z","PageNum":5,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"KerbMav","CreatedById":70338,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-13T19:51:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThree would never be enough until some things have become stock.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBut KER will be in always.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MR4Y","CreatedById":66897,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-13T23:59:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFAR, Deadly Reentry and Kerbal Alarm Clock\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"O-Doc","CreatedById":95453,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-14T08:26:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EEasy...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERPM\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVV\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHull Camera\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-14T09:39:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022O-Doc\u0022 data-cite=\u0022O-Doc\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EEasy...\u003Cp\u003ERPM\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVV\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHull Camera\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat is VV?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MircoMars","CreatedById":61811,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-14T11:09:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EKAC\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKAS\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ethen I\u0027d have to pick either MJ or ScanSAT... hmpf\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xrayfishx","CreatedById":76147,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-14T16:02:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFAR, DRE, KW.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s not that hard for me to choose these, but I would hate giving up Procedural Parts and FloorIt. And all the other 66 mods I have right now.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gristle","CreatedById":60589,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-14T17:06:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EKerbal Alarm Clock\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVOID\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERoot Selector\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWhat is VV?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EProbably Vessel Viewer - 3d Line drawings of your vessels, supports RasterProp and has a standalone viewer also.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Captain_Brian","CreatedById":114608,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-15T17:36:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI only NEED two:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E -Kerbal Engineer Redux\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E -Enhanced Navball\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECan\u0027t play without them. I need KER to design rockets and for the handy display of stage time and other data like time to apoapsis that you only find in map view. I need Enhanced Navball to actually read the Navball, otherwise I can\u0027t tell what\u0027s on it.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Uml\u00FCx","CreatedById":69703,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T12:44:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMechjeb\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKerbal Alarm Clock\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EProcedural Fairings\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"arsmith","CreatedById":110779,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-17T05:23:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KvickFlygarn87\u0022 data-cite=\u0022KvickFlygarn87\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EKER, KAC, and KAS.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESame again for me.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rainbowtrout","CreatedById":60253,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-17T06:46:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI install mods, but hardly use them, but sometimes I do. I would use these three.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-KAS (Really useful, base functionality!)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-MJ (I use it for things that I CAN do but I\u0027m just too lazy to do. Mostly. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E )\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-B9 (It\u0027s just so awesome....)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Jet","CreatedById":99880,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-17T08:06:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThree? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E Sir, do you know, you\u0027re a provocateur? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere are at least \u003Cstrong\u003Eseven\u003C/strong\u003E ABSOLUTELY ESSENTIAL mods:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEditor Extensions - absolute ass-savior when designing\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERoot Part Selector - absolute ass-savior when designing\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERCS Balancer - not as absolute as abovementioned but still ass-saver when designing something asymmetrical\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFAR \u002B DRE - somewhat realistic aerodynamics (stock is terrible)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EProcedural Fairings - you NEED fairings when you have realistic aerodynamics - get either those or hard-fixed ones from any big part pack\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMechJeb - flight telemetry, dV calculation, autopilot (or KER for dedicated luddites)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd with just those seven you\u0027ll still miss a lot. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHighly recommended mods: \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKWR\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERPM\u002BProbeControlRoom\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERT2 \u002B AIES (for antennas)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERealChute\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EScanSat\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETAC LS\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo that\u0027s 15 mods at least for comfortable play.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EVA_Reentry","CreatedById":156961,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T02:11:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSXT, Tweakscale, and hyper edit\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RA3236","CreatedById":150734,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T05:38:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLol \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0Kopernicus, KillAshleys KASE and DynamicTextureLoader.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"genericeventhandler","CreatedById":149557,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T08:20:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nMechJeb 2 \u00A0- Even though I only use Smart A.S.S and Ascent Guidence most of the time.\u00A0\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/111978-113-anatid-robotics-mumech-mechjeb-autopilot-258-22-jun-2016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDocking Port Alignment (navy fish)\u00A0\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/40423-11-docking-port-alignment-indicator-version-64-updated-05112016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSafeChute - Slows down timewarp when it\u0027s needed.\u00A0\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/90954-112-safechute-v191-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kreutzkevic","CreatedById":146514,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T09:25:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Kerbal Engineer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Kerbal Alarm Clock\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- NAvyfish\u0027s Docking Alignment Indicator\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"h0yer","CreatedById":112042,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T10:07:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E dependencies\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E suggestions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"evileye.x","CreatedById":153755,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T11:34:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003EKAC\u003C/abbr\u003E, Precise Node.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout those KSP is unplayable\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RA3236","CreatedById":150734,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T11:40:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold on... HUGE NECRO?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TK421d","CreatedById":104476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T18:38:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\neditor extensions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmechjeb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nproc parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut if i were to cheat, i\u0027d swap my master-mod for proc parts (which is basicly just hacked versions of about 15 diff parts mods down into 1 mod with just the stuff i use from them)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T18:46:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal Engineer, Scatterer, AnyRes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tyko","CreatedById":164179,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T20:23:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222649610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002275560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467027295\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022153755\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022evileye.x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn June 27, 2016 at 4:34 AM, evileye.x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003EKAC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, Precise Node.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout those KSP is unplayable\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree except I\u0027ve recently switched to Precise Maneuver instead. Very similar, but a few additional features.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T20:42:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMechjeb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal Joint Reinforcement\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVX Series II Engines (I might be biased)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"evileye.x","CreatedById":153755,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T05:14:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222652070\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002275560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467145399\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022164179\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tjt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, tjt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree except I\u0027ve recently switched to Precise Maneuver instead. Very similar, but a few additional features.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would love to switch as well, as features like plan circularize in one click is very nice to have,\u00A0\u00A0but it has no \u002Borbit - orbit buttons, not very convenient to plan rendezvous...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"storm_soldier2377","CreatedById":158054,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T16:49:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal Engineer, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E, and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}